text:
Kaho! Juri-chan! Good work,
practicing for the sports festival must be tough, huh~...!

An empty stomach... here,
have this...

Wow, croquette bread and a drink!
Looks delicious. Thank you!

A chilled towel...!
Feels so good!

So, we...!
We'd like to volunteer to be your managers...!

With Coach Juri and the manager,
I'll be a hundred times stronger!
